## PrepareLeapSporeUnsignedPsbtParams interface

Parameters required to generate an unsigned PSBT (Partially Signed Bitcoin Transaction) for leaping a spore from Bitcoin to CKB. This interface is used to estimate transaction fees before finalizing the transaction.

**Signature:**

```typescript
export interface PrepareLeapSporeUnsignedPsbtParams 
```
